                      <span>2003-03-09</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>The book itself was a good introduction, however I felt it didnt grab me, as a reader , well enough. Difficult to explain , I guess I can say the book didn't really grab my attention and make me want to go and meditate.<P>However, this book was a good introduction to meditation. If you already understand the fundamentals of meditation and know the background, I suggest you skip the book, otherwise go ahead and check it out, its worth it!</span>
                  
              
